Tabaraka allathee biyadihi almulku wahuwa ‘ala kulli shay-in qadeerun
Allathee khalaqa almawta waalhayata liyabluwakum ayyukum ahsanu ‘amalan wahuwa al’azeezu alghafooru
Allathee khalaqa sab’a samawatin tibaqan ma tara fee khalqi alrrahmani min tafawutin fairji’i albasara hal tara min futoorin
Thumma irji’i albasara karratayni yanqalib ilayka albasaru khasi-an wahuwa haseerun
Walaqad zayyanna alssamaa alddunya bimasabeeha waja’alnaha rujooman lilshshayateeni waa’tadna lahum ‘athaba alssa’eeri
Walillatheena kafaroo birabbihim ‘athabu jahannama wabi/sa almaseeru
Itha olqoo feeha sami’oo laha shaheeqan wahiya tafooru
Takadu tamayyazu mina alghaythi kullama olqiya feeha fawjun saalahum khazanatuha alam ya/tikum natheerun
Qaloo bala qad jaana natheerun fakaththabna waqulna ma nazzala Allahu min shay-in in antum illa fee dalalin kabeerin
Waqaloo law kunna nasma’u aw na’qilu ma kunna fee as-habi alssa’eeri
Fai’tarafoo bithanbihim fasuhqan li-as-habi alssa’eeri
Inna allatheena yakhshawna rabbahum bialghaybi lahum maghfiratun waajrun kabeerun
Waasirroo qawlakum awi ijharoo bihi innahu ‘aleemun bithati alssudoori
Ala ya’lamu man khalaqa wahuwa allateefu alkhabeeru
Huwa allathee ja’ala lakumu al-arda thaloolan faimshoo fee manakibiha wakuloo min rizqihi wa-ilayhi alnnushooru
Aamintum man fee alssama-i an yakhsifa bikumu al-arda fa-itha hiya tamooru
Am amintum man fee alssama-i an yursila ‘alaykum hasiban fasata’lamoona kayfa natheeri
Walaqad kaththaba allatheena min qablihim fakayfa kana nakeeri
Awa lam yaraw ila alttayri fawqahum saffatin wayaqbidna ma yumsikuhunna illa alrrahmanu innahu bikulli shay-in baseerun
Amman hatha allathee huwa jundun lakum yansurukum min dooni alrrahmani ini alkafiroona illa fee ghuroorin
Amman hatha allathee yarzuqukum in amsaka rizqahu bal lajjoo fee ‘utuwwin wanufoorin
Afaman yamshee mukibban ‘ala wajhihi ahda amman yamshee sawiyyan ‘ala siratin mustaqeemin
Qul huwa allathee anshaakum waja’ala lakumu alssam’a waal-absara waal-afidata qaleelan ma tashkuroona
Qul huwa allathee tharaakum fee al-ardi wa-ilayhi tuhsharoona
Wayaqooloona mata hatha alwa’du in kuntum sadiqeena
Qul innama al’ilmu ‘inda Allahi wa-innama ana natheerun mubeenun
Falamma raawhu zulfatan see-at wujoohu allatheena kafaroo waqeela hatha allathee kuntum bihi tadda’oona
Qul araaytum in ahlakaniya Allahu waman ma’iya aw rahimana faman yujeeru alkafireena min ‘athabin aleemin
Qul huwa alrrahmanu amanna bihi wa’alayhi tawakkalna fasata’lamoona man huwa fee dalalin mubeenin
Qul araaytum in asbaha maokum ghawran faman ya/teekum bima-in ma’eenin